item.description: I study bioinformatics since Oct‘2018 in Munich with a research interest in human genetics and cancer biology. Before that I received a master’s degree in biology at the LMU Munich. During my studies, I focused on molecular and cell biology and protein biochemistry. I recently joined the Chair of Experimental Bioinformatics as a Hiwi to work on the diseasome project for a better understanding of a disease-gene interactions.
